from the reservoir is used to provide drinking water for the city of [[Kermanshah]] in the amount of {{Convert|63000000|m3|acre.ft|0|abbr=on}} annually. Construction on the dam began in 1992 and was completed in 2004.<ref>{{cite web|title=Gavoshan Dam and Conveyance Tunnel|url=http://www.mahabghodss.com/project/dhp/p-Gavoshan.ASP|publisher=Mahab Ghodss Consulting|accessdate=4 July 2011|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20111026170902/http://www.mahabghodss.com/project/dhp/p-Gavoshan.ASP|archivedate=26 October 2011|df=}}</ref> It was inaugurated by Iran's President [[Mohammad Khatami]] on 13 February 2005.<ref>{{cite web|title=Gavoshan Dam Inaugurated|url=http://www.shana.ir/45226-en.html|publisher=Shana|accessdate=4 July 2011|date=13 February 2005|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120406043820/http://www.shana.ir/45226-en.html|archivedate=6 April 2012|df=}}</ref>
